      ],
      "text": "Twelve years prior to Avatar Korra's arrival in Republic City, the mansion was broken into and robbed by the Agni Kai Triad. A member of the triad killed Yasuko, Hiroshi's wife, during the break-in."
    },
    {
      "body": "In 170 ${link_0}, after ${link_1}'s ${link_2} on the ${link_3} forced ${link_4} and ${link_5} to leave the attic they called home, they moved into the ${link_6} mansion at Asami's invitation. She did not directly ask her father if they could stay, but stated that she would clear it with him later. The three, along with ${link_7}, were swimming in the mansion's pool when Korra arrived, though the Avatar quickly left the estate after overhearing Hiroshi Sato planning what may have been an ${link_8} strike over the phone.",
