      "section": [
        "Sato estate",
        "History"
      ],
      "text": "In 171 AG, after their house in Ba Sing Se was destroyed during the anarchy in the Earth Kingdom, Asami allowed Mako and Bolin's family from their father's side to stay at the mansion. Three years later, Asami, Mako, and Korra took Prince Wu to the estate as well, where they hoped he would be safe from further kidnapping attempts by Kuvira's men."
